videos.description: ISU vs. TTU both miss shots at the end of the game to force the game into overtime.
videos.headline: ISU vs. TTU both miss shots at the end of the game to force the game into overtime.

videos.description: OT (3:17) ISU Deonte Burton made Layup.
videos.headline: D. Burton made layup after Monte Morris gets the offensive rebound.

videos.description: Texas Tech's Keenan Evans puts up the deep 3-pointer from almost half court that goes in before the shot clock goes off to give the Red Raiders the lead in overtime.
videos.headline: Evans beats the shot clock from away downtown

videos.description: Iowa State's last chance in overtime doesn't fall and Texas Tech holds on for the upset that signals another court storming by the students in the Big 12.
videos.headline: Another Big 12 upset, another Big 12 court storming
